	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Unfortunately, that schematic is missing the requisite signature bytes that games use to detect the Four Score. You'll need to increase the counters from 4 bits (each half of a '393) to 5 bits, use 74'153s instead of 74'157s, and add two shift registers.<br /><br />But it's pretty close.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


